---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="实战项目">
  <div class="mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400">🎯 实战项目</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
      通过完整的项目实战，巩固所学知识，积累开发经验
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-8">
    <!-- Project 1 -->
    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 hover:border-green-500 transition-colors">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-green-400">
            <a href="/projects/platformer-2d" class="hover:underline">2D 平台跳跃游戏</a>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
            完整的 2D 平台跳跃游戏，包含角色控制、敌人 AI、收集品、关卡设计、死亡与重生系统。
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">
            <span>⏱️ 8-10 小时</span>
            <span>📊 难度：⭐⭐⭐</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">CharacterBody2D</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Animation</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">TileMap</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Audio</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Project 2 -->
    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 hover:border-green-500 transition-colors">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-green-400">
            <a href="/projects/fps-3d" class="hover:underline">3D 第一人称探索</a>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
            3D 第一人称视角游戏，包含角色控制器、相机系统、交互系统、环境探索、简单的谜题设计。
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">
            <span>⏱️ 10-12 小时</span>
            <span>📊 难度：⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">CharacterBody3D</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Camera3D</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">RayCast</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Lighting</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Project 3 -->
    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 hover:border-green-500 transition-colors">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-green-400">
            <a href="/projects/turn-based-combat" class="hover:underline">回合制战斗系统</a>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
            完整的回合制战斗系统，包含角色属性、技能系统、战斗 UI、敌人 AI、战斗流程管理。
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">
            <span>⏱️ 6-8 小时</span>
            <span>📊 难度：⭐⭐⭐</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">State Machine</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">UI System</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Data Management</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Project 4 -->
    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 hover:border-green-500 transition-colors">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">4</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-green-400">
            <a href="/projects/ui-system" class="hover:underline">完整 UI 系统实现</a>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
            专业的游戏 UI 系统，包含主菜单、设置界面、背包系统、对话框、HUD、UI 动画与过渡。
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">
            <span>⏱️ 8-10 小时</span>
            <span>📊 难度：⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Control Nodes</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Themes</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Animation</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Localization</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Project 5 -->
    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 hover:border-green-500 transition-colors">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">5</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-green-400">
            <a href="/projects/save-system" class="hover:underline">存档与数据管理系统</a>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
            通用的存档系统实现，包含数据序列化、多存档位、自动保存、数据迁移、加密存储。
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">
            <span>⏱️ 4-6 小时</span>
            <span>📊 难度：⭐⭐⭐</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Serialization</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">File I/O</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Encryption</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Project 6 -->
    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 hover:border-green-500 transition-colors">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">6</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-green-400">
            <a href="/projects/multiplayer-demo" class="hover:underline">多人游戏演示</a>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
            简单的多人游戏示例，包含网络连接、玩家同步、房间系统、聊天功能、基础游戏逻辑。
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">
            <span>⏱️ 12-15 小时</span>
            <span>📊 难度：⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Multiplayer</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">RPC</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Networking</span>
            <span class="bg-green-900 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Sync</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-900 to-blue-900 rounded-lg p-8 border border-green-700">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">💡 项目学习建议</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-gray-300">
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">📌 按顺序学习</h4>
        <p>建议按照难度递进的顺序完成项目，每个项目都建立在前置知识之上。</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">🔧 先模仿再创新</h4>
        <p>先完整实现教程内容，然后尝试添加自己的功能和改进。</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">📝 记录问题</h4>
        <p>遇到问题时记录解决方案，建立自己的知识库。</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">🎮 完成比完美重要</h4>
        <p>先做出可玩的版本，再逐步完善。不要陷入过度优化的陷阱。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
